name: Damali Haverland
coverLetter: I've been trimming for a couple weeks now, but I learned fast. I can trim about a pound and a half in 8 to 10 hours depending on the bud. I am looking for a place to park my car and that provides at least 1 to 2 meals a day. I am also looking for a place that pays between $150 and $200 per pound.
